~ waveforms — harmonic constructions over a fundamental
~ invoke "waveforms" to bring these incantations into your scroll.

~ a sweep upward across an octave in eight steps
incant sweep takes f
  let step be f
  repeat 8
    burn step for 0.15
    scale step by 1.0905
    drift 0.05
    breathe
  end
end

~ stack a tone with its third and fifth — a sounded triad
incant triad takes f
  burn f
  burn f scale by 1.25
  burn f scale by 1.5
end
